      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 31.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃああっ！？　どうして私の名前を！？\nわひっ、肩に、手がぁっ、手がぁ……きゅう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5650.612004499997,
          "startTime": 38.7172786712
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 37.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.5520922342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すずにゃーーーーん！？\nあーあ、だから開けちゃダメって言ったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7666722615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなもびっくりさせ過ぎだよ\nすずにゃんは芽衣の一番の親友なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1000055949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 54.3520924884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "気になるのは分かるけれど\nこんな風にびっくりさせるのはダメだよー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 60.0187591551
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "う、うぅぅ……芽衣……？\nだ、誰と話して、いるんですの……きゅう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0666725158,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11074.3531552,
          "startTime": 71.0931123103
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hauntedhouse-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 71.0931123103
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 73.1554032006
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 73.1554032006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……うぅうぅぅん……お肉っ！\nお肉の匂いですのっ！　って、あれ、ここは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 86.4610630143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、まだ焼いてないのによく分かるね！\n今、すずにゃんの大好きな焼肉の準備してるよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9000058491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 97.6784191766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、それは嬉しい……\nじゃなくてっ！　わ、私、確かさっきまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 106.1952901202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "怖い夢でも見ちゃったのかな？\nずっとうなされてたから……よしよーし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6738.043213099999,
          "startTime": 112.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7371.376546500002,
          "startTime": 113.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 112.3000058491
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 116.228621419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、子供扱いしないでくださいましっ！\nでも夢でしたのね。あんなびっくりした夢は初めて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5333346048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 127.6436323164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "びっくり……？　はっ！　あれは天啓でしたのね！\n見つけましたわよ、芽衣。私達のすべき、新しい演出！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0000012714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 134.0000012714
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamaliving-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 140.4885758081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "よーく聞くんですのよっ！\n今度のライブでは、『驚き』をテーマにして――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6333346048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4136552492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 149.815129121
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 149.815129121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー！　芽衣達、『わんにゃんツインズ』の\nライブに来てくれて、ありがとー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2333346048,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6651.538308399978,
          "startTime": 157.4000012714
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 158.548462963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei Hayasaka",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣だけがステージにいて不思議だよね\n大丈夫、すずにゃんも来てるからっ！　ほら、あそこ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.7849603763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s4",
      "startTime": 167.4495844839
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s4",
      "startTime": 167.4495844839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん！　客席からサプライズ登場ですわ～！\nみなさん、びっくりしていただけましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.433331553,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-04.m4a",
          "delay": 451.5405975000135,
          "startTime": 168.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.332061900006,
          "startTime": 176.0666636149
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s4",
      "startTime": 177.2699254034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、隣に私がいるなんて思わなかったのでは\nなくて？　気配を消すの、大変だったんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.0666567483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_13_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "でもサプライズはまだまだ残ってますわよ\nみなさん、芽衣を見てくださいまし！",
